<p align="left"><font size="3" face="ms sans serif" color="#000080">
<b>#7 - The Intellectual</b><br>
You are a searcher. Always probing for hidden information, you find it
difficult to accept things at face value. Emotions don't sway your
decisions. Questioning everything in life, you don't like to be 
questioned yourself. You're never off to a fast start; your motto is 
'slow and steady wins the race'. You come across as being very
knowledgeable and somewhat of a philosopher, and maybe somewhat of a
loner. You are technically inclined, and you love to uncover secrets. 
That combination makes you a great researcher. Your only problem is
that you live in your own world. You need to learn what is acceptable
