You are a natural entertainer. You are very caring and generous, giving
away your last dollar to help someone. With your charm, you have no
problem making friends; no one is a stranger to you. You have so many
different personalities that people around you have a hard time
understanding you sometimes. You are like a chamelion, ever changing
